Fury is a very humble, talented and a hardworking guy. I have never underestimated Fury's abilities or his mindset. I have been supporting him since day 1 and would continue to do so. I supported him during both the fights and guess what he backed up what he said.
Fury is a man of his words. He went to America fought against the most feared Heavyweight in the division infront of a panel of 3 American judges and an american refree. He goes on to stop Wilder in an exceptional fashion while also being ahead on all judges scorecards, won everyone's heart and goes on to sing along with the entire crowd after his victory. What a Legend! <3
And the new!!! 👑
